item.title: #Uttarakhand CM #PushkarSinghD
item.description: #Uttarakhand CM #PushkarSinghDhami announces a big push on jobs and education, distributing appointment letters to 72 new Assistant Professors and launching a portal offering Rs 50,000 grants for meritorious students.

item.title: The only #cheetah from #Namibi
item.description: The only #cheetah from #Namibia, to survive wilderness in #MadhyaPradesh’s #KunoNationalPark was found dead with officials suspected drowning as the cause of death. Read more here: https://www.hindustantimes.com/.../only-free-ranging...
